name: Magnarok
description:
Magnarok was forged by an alien dwarven clan on the volcanic planet Tarterix in the outskirts of the Andromedus galaxy. 

After feuding clans on the planet were embroiled in bitter 20 year civil war the victor's brutal leader Bronson was named high chief and claimed Magnarok as his own. 

It is said Magnarok's unbreakable blade has the ability to swell to volcanic temperatures in the heat of battles yet it's hilt is made of a rare unknown material that dissipates all heat and has superior grip for ultimate weapon handling. 

The weapon was stolen by Braze and his elite force during in a covert black ops mission along with many other valuable items but rather than accept pay for the mission was allowed to keep the sword as his prize.

Attack: + 20
Health: + 15
